-- Citigroup CEO Pandit Says Africa Has a Major Role to Play as Trade Booms
-- B y   R e n e e   B o n o r c h i s
-- 2010-12-07T15:27:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-07/citigroup-ceo-pandit-says-africa-has-a-major-role-to-play-as-trade-booms.html
Citigroup Inc.’s Chief Executive
Officer Vikram Pandit said Africa has a “major role” to play
in a world that’s seeing “exponential growth” in trade between
emerging markets.  More South African companies will expand on the rest of the
continent and Citigroup is ready to support them with a range of
products, Pandit told reporters in Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Renee Bonorchis in Johannesburg at 
 rbonorchis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
